import React from "react"
import { Row, Col } from "reactstrap"
import Breadcrumbs from "../../components/@vuexy/breadCrumbs/BreadCrumb"
import QuestionsSearch from "../pages/faq/QuestionsSearch"

// import "../../../assets/scss/pages/faq.scss"

import "../../assets/scss/pages/faq.scss"

class testPage extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <React.Fragment>
        <Breadcrumbs
          breadCrumbTitle="FAQ"
          breadCrumbParent="Test"
          breadCrumbParent2="Page"
          breadCrumbActive="TestPage"
        />
        <Row>
          <Col sm="12">
            <QuestionsSearch />
          </Col>
        </Row>
      </React.Fragment>
    )
  }
}

export default testPage
